          Innovation Massive Solutions (IMS) provides professional website development using cutting-edge technologies. 
          We deliver secure, scalable, and responsive digital solutions to support your business transformation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="footer-title">Navigation</h3>
        <ul class="footer-links">
          <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="/products">Products & Pricing</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="footer-title">Contact Us</h3>
        <ul class="footer-links" style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope" style="color: var(--accent-primary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> contact@ims.com</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone" style="color: var(--accent-primary); margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i> +62 812-3456-7890</li>
